headline: Visa Inc.’s (V) Acceptance Of Modern Financial Technology Makes It A Growth Play

headline: The Week CEOs Bent the Knee to Trump
summary: Companies abandoned Donald Trump after the Jan. 6, 2021, riot. Now, they are rushing to curry favor with the president-elect as he prepares to return to the White House.
